author: Steven Overly
title: Facebook shuts down anti-quarantine protests at states' request
description: The social network has already removed protest messages in California, New Jersey and Nebraska.
content:
Alexander Koerner/Getty Images
Facebook is blocking anti-quarantine protesters from using the site to organize in-person gatherings in states that require residents to stay in their homes due to the coronavirus pandemic.
